      <title>英伟达 2024 年红火开启亮点，创标普 500 强新纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/nvidia-s-red-hot-2024-start-a-bright-spot-as-s-p-500-eyes-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从一项指标来看，英伟达公司迎来了有史以来最强劲的一年开局，继续保持强劲反弹，股价在 2023 年上涨了近 240%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/nvidia-s-red-hot-2024-start-a-bright-spot-as-s-p-500-eyes-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apple 将关闭 121 人的圣地亚哥 AI 团队进行重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/apple-to-shutter-121-person-san-diego-ai-team-in-reorganization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司正在关闭圣地亚哥一个与人工智能业务相关的 121 人团队，导致许多员工面临被解雇的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/apple-to-shutter-121-person-san-diego-ai-team-in-reorganization</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:03:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假期周末极端寒冷袭击美国大片地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/us-weather-this-weekend-extreme-cold-hammers-wide-swath-of-country-over-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冬季的严寒正在让美国大片地区变得麻木，给南部的德克萨斯州带来了雨夹雪、降雪和冻雨，考验了当地的电网，甚至迫使气温适宜的布法罗推迟了周日的 NFL 比赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/us-weather-this-weekend-extreme-cold-hammers-wide-swath-of-country-over-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 19:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 激励 NASA 为登月计划中的小事故做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/nasa-was-inspired-by-elon-musk-s-spacex-and-built-missteps-into-moonshot-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，五十多年来首个美国制造的月球着陆器在抵达太空后不久就遭遇严重故障，这一消息最初引起了人们的震惊。但美国宇航局已经做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/nasa-was-inspired-by-elon-musk-s-spacex-and-built-missteps-into-moonshot-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
